    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm so excited to list this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels brand new! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cleaned, and looks stunning inside and out. You won't find a single flaw on this beauty. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically fresh off the showroom floor, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
