    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute time capsule for the most discerning collector. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did on the delivery floor. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or rock chips, while the factory wheels remain entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin retains its 'new car' scent; the premium upholstery shows no signs of wear, and the dashboard is free from any fading or tactile degradation. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standard, backed by a comprehensive file of service records from the original dealer. Garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. If you are looking for a flawless example that requires zero correction or maintenance, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
